text: Pierre Duprat (born 26 November 1989 in Agen) is a French judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 73 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Denis Iartcev. ==References== Category:Sportspeople from Agen Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:French male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of France Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:European Games competitors for France Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games
